    {
      "id": "724624",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "[已注销]",
        "uid": null
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t东亚女权也是这样，极端仇男，甚至仇视男孩，仇视公猫，仇视一切y染色体<br/>\n东亚男女对立严重，都缺乏换位思考共情能力，还自我意识过剩，容易被侵犯。我也有这些毛病，还是多学学西方人爱与包容吧\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2024-01-30",
      "agree_count": 0,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "724125",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "熱帶魚",
        "uid": "120269"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t西方坐在談判桌的前提是，他可以用錢砸死你。兩個人打嘴炮吹水，誰都不會服誰。只有把錢真的提出來，才會老老實實説話。中國人沒有錢，那麽中國人只能用命來抵押了。\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2024-01-29",
      "agree_count": 0,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "727253",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "海淀居民",
        "uid": "120458"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\tThen what is the common ground for the leftists and the rightists to proceed their debates and negotiations? Without no doubt it's the solid system of democracy, the lack of which leads to inevitable conflicts and bloods among political powers.<br/>\nIn China's case, you can't expect the dissidents to \"sit down and have a talk\" with the communists, obviously, only is coming out that the former will get arrested with the latter punching their fists and congratulating this victory without costs.\t\t</div>",
